docs.title: Welcome to the Project
docs.text: Welcome to the official project documentation. Here you'll find everything from setup instructions to detailed API references.

docs.title: System Architecture
docs.text: This section explains the high-level system architecture.

docs.title: Components
docs.text:
1. Frontend: React-based UI
  2. Backend: Python Flask API
  3. Database: PostgreSQL
  4. CI/CD: GitHub Actions

docs.title: Workflow
docs.text:
1. User sends request
  2. Frontend handles UI logic
  3. Backend processes request
  4. Database stores/retrieves data
  5. Response returned to frontend
